#7300
@@WThe Pass Office Annex@@N~
@@WA squat stone building pressed against the south face of Midgaard's wall, the annex
serves as the overflow station for pass checks during heavy southern traffic. Stamped
advisories cover every flat surface, most too faded to read. A single lantern hangs
from an iron bracket, its flame inadequate for the paper-clutter inside.@@N
