#7301
@@WThe Eastern Gate Booth@@N~
@@WThis narrow checkpoint booth is planted just east of the main gate road. A waist-high
counter bisects the interior, worn smooth by generations of arms resting on it. Variance
postings are pinned in rows above the counter, each describing a different category of
incident logged on the southern approach. The booth is staffed but the staff may not be
listening.@@N
