#7302
@@WThe Southern Wild Gate Approach@@N~
@@WMidgaard's southern gate rises at your back, its arch carved with the liability language
of three separate civic eras. The road ahead narrows almost immediately, the paving
stones giving way to packed dirt before the first tree line. @@WStamped advisories on
both gateposts warn of variance events, escort requirements, and route closures since the
last survey. @@bA patrol trace in the dirt — boot prints, a drag mark — points south
and does not return. The city noise fades within a dozen steps.@@N
