is cold and perfectly still. @@pThe canopy overhead is densest here, and the
light is only a diffuse amber gloom. @@pSomething in the stillness feels
attentive — as if the space is listening to whoever enters, cataloguing details
for some later purpose. @@pThis is the domain of the Marrow Ledger of Ninth Acre.@@N
